    "uen": "200201652N",
    "description": "<p>Adsan Law LLC were first established as Yeo-Leong &amp; Peh in 1987, a partnership which had developed significantly since its humble beginning into a mid-sized law corporation. In 1997, we set up a representative office in Shanghai, China. We also have a wide network of associated offices in various countries. In 2002, we became Yeo-Leong &amp; Peh LLC, a limited liability company that developed an international perspective with the ability to meet client needs not only in Singapore but also around the region. As part of rebranding, the name was changed to Adsan Law LLC in 2020.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We provide one-stop, customised legal services to individuals and corporate entities. We are one of the first to develop a proprietary legal case management system in Singapore. We are strongly committed to modern technological innovations and have integrated the latest computer technology into our systems and operations. This enables our teams to provide optimum legal services to our clients in Singapore and across the globe. We believe in working closely with our clients to consistently delivering high quality legal services in a reliable, integrated and efficient manner.</p>",
